headlines.description: — Tyrese Maxey scored 43 points to lead a Philadelphia 76ers team without injured Joel Embiid and Paul George to a 118-104 win over the Los Angeles...
headlines.shortLinkText: Tyrese Maxey scores 43 to lift 76ers past LeBron, Lakers 118-104

headlines.description: — Jalen Green scored 12 of his 25 points in the third quarter and the Houston Rockets avoided a late collapse to beat the Atlanta Hawks 100-96 on Tuesday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Green scores 25 and Rockets hold off Hawks 100-96 for fourth straight victory

events.name: Utah Jazz at Golden State Warriors

headlines.description: — Dennis Schroder scored 23 points with five 3-pointers, Brandin Podziemski contributed 20 points off the bench with Stephen Curry sitting out to rest his troublesome knees, and the Golden State Warriors beat the stumbling Utah Jazz 114-103 on Tuesday...
headlines.shortLinkText: Dennis Schroder scores 23 points with Stephen Curry out as Warriors beat Jazz 114-103

events.name: Milwaukee Bucks at Portland Trail Blazers

headlines.description: — Deni Avdija scored a season-high 30 points and the Portland Trail Blazers bested former teammate Damian Lillard with a 125-112 victory over the Milwaukee Bucks on Tuesday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Avdija scores 30 as the Blazers top former teammate Lillard and the Bucks 125-112
